import React, { useState } from 'react' import Stat from '../Components/Stat' const CandidateDash = () => { const [infos,setInfos]=useState({lastName:"",firstName:"",login:"",number:"",picture:"",cv:"",emailReceive:"",field:"",interviewCount:0,demandCount:0}) return (

{`${infos.firstName} ${infos.lastName}`}

{infos.field}

E-mail : {infos.login}

Number : {infos.number}

Receive Emails ? {infos.emailReceive?"Yes":"No"}

) } export default CandidateDash
